Perfect authentical food
We tried this place based on the advice from the travelers. It was so authentical place, but don't expect any fancy place. Food was perfect, I am not sure, if there is more to choose, but we took banh xeo. It was the best what I had in Vietnam. Be brave to go there. It is something like must to visit in Da Nang.
