Best Banh xeo in all of Vietnam!
Very busy restaurant that has only 6 things on the menu, we wanted to try Banh Xeo based on a food blogger's recommendation.. boy she was spot on. The whole experience of wrapping fresh ingredients, hot creps is great and the sauce is to die for! A real flavour explosion in your mouth, if in Da Nang do not miss this place.
