Lunasolhk
Hong Kong, China
203102
Reviewed April 3, 2019
Must eat in Da Nang
My friend who frequently travels to Da Nang for work recommend this one for us and we are not disappointed!
The banh xeo are really special and tasty. The sauce just topped everything up. If you are not sure how to start, just look around and follow what other customers do.
We took a taxi to get directly from the hotel. The restaurant is down at the end of an alley. Just walk straight down. This restaurant is really famous among local and tourists so everyone will be able to point you the right direction.
Date of visit: March 2019
