Believe the hype!
The bomb. That‚Äôs it. Eat slowly, figure out how to make the perfect bite for yourself. The standard way of eating this is to wrap the rice paper around the pancake and add other stuff. But that‚Äôs not the only way to eat it. Definitely recommend the basil beef as a side dish. And the skewers are awesome too. The pickled radish is very important, in my opinion.
I reckon the secret to the peanut sauce is minced pork and liver?
