Eva L
Cupertino, California
118136
Reviewed December 30, 2018
Delicious banh xeo in the middle of the city
This is is very high on the list of must try local food. The place is at the end of a small alley. The sign is big, you won't miss it. I think they only serve two items, banh xeo and pork skewer. One order consist of four banh xeo costs 50K vnd. Pork skewers come in group of five, 5K vnd per skewer. For two people, one order of banh xeo and two orders of skewers, plus two drinks, is about 130 vnd. The food is delicious. Wrap the banh Xeo and pork skewer in rice sheet and lecture, dip in the sauce. You won't regret!
Date of visit: December 2018
